====Verb====
{{en-verb|puns|punning|punned}}

# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To [[beat]]; [[strike]] with force; [[ram]]; [[pound]], as in a mortar; reduce to powder.
#* Shakespeare
#*: He would '''pun''' thee into shivers with his fist.

===Etymology 2===
